work flow 
Admin
  ↓
Create Project
  ↓
Project Manager
  ↓
Create Modules
  ↓
Create Tasks
  ↓
Assign Tasks to Developers
  ↓
Developer works on task
  ↓
Tester tests the task
  ↓
Tester reports Bug
  ↓
Developer fixes bug
  ↓
Tester verifies bug
  ↓
Task marked completed


------------------------------->
dependency order of bugtracking sys.
User → Project → Module → Task → Bug → TimeLog